    "title": {
      "rendered": "10 Must-Know Stats About COVID-19 Donors"
    },
    "content": {
      "rendered": "<h2 style=\"text-align: left;\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-26524\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/COVID-19-Donors-to-Charity.jpg?resize=960%2C480\" alt=\"\" width=\"960\" height=\"480\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/COVID-19-Donors-to-Charity.jpg?w=1024&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/COVID-19-Donors-to-Charity.jpg?resize=300%2C150&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/COVID-19-Donors-to-Charity.jpg?resize=768%2C384&amp;ssl=1 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\" /></h2>\n<p>The 2020 Global Trends in Giving Survey closed June 1 and the full results will be released September 14 in the third edition of the <a href=\"http://www.nptechforgood.com/research/\"><strong>Global Trends in Giving Report</strong></a>. 7,008 survey respondents from 81 countries indicated in the survey that they had donated in response to the COVID-19 pandemic and some characteristics of these donors are listed below.</p>\n<p>It&#8217;s worth noting that 68% of the COVID-19 donors were female, 31% male. 41% were Baby Boomers, 24% Millennials, 22% Gen X, 11% Matures, and 2% Gen Z.</p>\n<hr />\n<h2>1) The top three preferred methods of giving are online (80.5%), bank/wire transfer (18.6%), and direct mail/post (14.4%).</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-26506\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Preferred-Method-of-Donating.jpg?resize=833%2C819\" alt=\"\" width=\"833\" height=\"819\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Preferred-Method-of-Donating.jpg?w=833&amp;ssl=1 833w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Preferred-Method-of-Donating.jpg?resize=300%2C295&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Preferred-Method-of-Donating.jpg?resize=768%2C755&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Preferred-Method-of-Donating.jpg?resize=75%2C75&amp;ssl=1 75w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Preferred-Method-of-Donating.jpg?resize=80%2C80&amp;ssl=1 80w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 833px) 100vw, 833px\" /></p>\n<h2>2) 53.6% of COVID-19 donors are enrolled in a recurring giving program.</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-26507\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Monthly-Donors-to-Nonprofits.jpg?resize=829%2C684\" alt=\"\" width=\"829\" height=\"684\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Monthly-Donors-to-Nonprofits.jpg?w=829&amp;ssl=1 829w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Monthly-Donors-to-Nonprofits.jpg?resize=300%2C248&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Monthly-Donors-to-Nonprofits.jpg?resize=768%2C634&amp;ssl=1 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 829px) 100vw, 829px\" /></p>\n<h2>3) 49.7% have donated to a crowdfunding campaign benefiting a nonprofit within the last 12 months.</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-26509\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Crowdfunding-for-Nonprofits.jpg?resize=828%2C567\" alt=\"\" width=\"828\" height=\"567\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Crowdfunding-for-Nonprofits.jpg?w=828&amp;ssl=1 828w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Crowdfunding-for-Nonprofits.jpg?resize=300%2C205&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Crowdfunding-for-Nonprofits.jpg?resize=768%2C526&amp;ssl=1 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 828px) 100vw, 828px\" /></p>\n<h2>4) 12.3% have created a peer-to-peer fundraising campaign benefiting a nonprofit within the last 12 months.</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-26510\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Peer-to-Peer-Fundraising-COVID-Donors.jpg?resize=826%2C569\" alt=\"\" width=\"826\" height=\"569\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Peer-to-Peer-Fundraising-COVID-Donors.jpg?w=826&amp;ssl=1 826w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Peer-to-Peer-Fundraising-COVID-Donors.jpg?resize=300%2C207&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Peer-to-Peer-Fundraising-COVID-Donors.jpg?resize=768%2C529&amp;ssl=1 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 826px) 100vw, 826px\" /></p>\n<h2>5) 20.9% of COVID-19 donors also donated to a nonprofit on #GivingTuesday 2019.</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-26512\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/GIvingTuesday-2019-COVID.jpg?resize=824%2C583\" alt=\"\" width=\"824\" height=\"583\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/GIvingTuesday-2019-COVID.jpg?w=824&amp;ssl=1 824w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/GIvingTuesday-2019-COVID.jpg?resize=300%2C212&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/GIvingTuesday-2019-COVID.jpg?resize=768%2C543&amp;ssl=1 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 824px) 100vw, 824px\" /></p>\n<h2>6) 32.6% give to nonprofits located outside of their country of residence. The top three countries are the U.S. (24.9%), Canada (9.7%), and India (4.2%).</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-26514\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Give-outside-country-of-residence-COVID-donors.jpg?resize=828%2C528\" alt=\"\" width=\"828\" height=\"528\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Give-outside-country-of-residence-COVID-donors.jpg?w=828&amp;ssl=1 828w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Give-outside-country-of-residence-COVID-donors.jpg?resize=300%2C191&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Give-outside-country-of-residence-COVID-donors.jpg?resize=768%2C490&amp;ssl=1 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 828px) 100vw, 828px\" /></p>\n<h2>7) 66.7% have volunteered for a nonprofit within the last 12 months. 74% donated to the nonprofit that they volunteered for.</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-26513\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Volunteer-COVID-donors.jpg?resize=830%2C529\" alt=\"\" width=\"830\" height=\"529\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Volunteer-COVID-donors.jpg?w=830&amp;ssl=1 830w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Volunteer-COVID-donors.jpg?resize=300%2C191&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Volunteer-COVID-donors.jpg?resize=768%2C489&amp;ssl=1 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 830px) 100vw, 830px\" /></p>\n<h2>8) 32% of COVID-19 donors have donated through Facebook Fundraising Tools. Of those, 88% said they are likely to do it again.</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-26515\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Facebook-Fundraising-COVID-Donors.jpg?resize=827%2C644\" alt=\"\" width=\"827\" height=\"644\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Facebook-Fundraising-COVID-Donors.jpg?w=827&amp;ssl=1 827w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Facebook-Fundraising-COVID-Donors.jpg?resize=300%2C234&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Facebook-Fundraising-COVID-Donors.jpg?resize=768%2C598&amp;ssl=1 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 827px) 100vw, 827px\" /></p>\n<h2>9) 10.7% have donated through Instagram Fundraising Tools. Of those, 93% said they are likely to do it again.</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-26516\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Instagram-Fundraising-Tools-COVID-donors.jpg?resize=828%2C644\" alt=\"\" width=\"828\" height=\"644\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Instagram-Fundraising-Tools-COVID-donors.jpg?w=828&amp;ssl=1 828w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Instagram-Fundraising-Tools-COVID-donors.jpg?resize=300%2C233&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Instagram-Fundraising-Tools-COVID-donors.jpg?resize=768%2C597&amp;ssl=1 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 828px) 100vw, 828px\" /></p>\n<h2>10) 64.8% of COVID-19 donors say that regular email communication about the impact of their donation is most likely to inspire them to give repeatedly to an organization.</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-26519\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/How-to-Thank-COVID-19-Donors.jpg?resize=829%2C660\" alt=\"\" width=\"829\" height=\"660\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/How-to-Thank-COVID-19-Donors.jpg?w=829&amp;ssl=1 829w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/How-to-Thank-COVID-19-Donors.jpg?resize=300%2C239&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/How-to-Thank-COVID-19-Donors.jpg?resize=768%2C611&amp;ssl=1 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 829px) 100vw, 829px\" /></p>\n<hr />\n<p><span style=\"color: #c30437;\"><a style=\"color: #c30437;\" href=\"http://www.nptechforgood.com/101-best-practices-for-nonprofits/\"><em><strong>101 Best Practices for Nonprofits</strong></em></a></span> is a year-long blog and webinar series (written and presented by <span style=\"color: #c30437;\"><strong><a style=\"color: #c30437;\" href=\"http://www.nptechforgood.com/heather-mansfield/\">Heather Mansfield</a></strong></span>) on website design, email marketing, online fundraising, and social media best practices for nonprofits, NGOs, and charities worldwide. Sign up for\u00a0<a href=\"https://mailchi.mp/nptechforgood/news\"><strong><span style=\"color: #c30437;\">Nonprofit Tech for Good\u2019s email newsletter</span></strong></a>\u00a0to be alerted of new posts.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.nptechforgood.com/101-best-practices-for-nonprofits/\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-25066\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/1200-x-600-Banner.png?resize=960%2C480\" alt=\"\" width=\"960\" height=\"480\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/1200-x-600-Banner.png?w=1200&amp;ssl=1 1200w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/1200-x-600-Banner.png?resize=300%2C150&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/1200-x-600-Banner.png?resize=1024%2C512&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/1200-x-600-Banner.png?resize=768%2C384&amp;ssl=1 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\" /></a></p>\n",
